      "mode": "character",
      "text": "Morning (10:00:00) in the Restricted Archives\u2014you pause in your examination of the mysterious tome and take a proper look around the chamber.\n\nThe Restricted Archives stretch before you in a cathedral of knowledge, though one that has seen better centuries. Towering oak shelves, blackened with age, rise fifteen feet to the vaulted ceiling, their ledges thick with accumulated dust. Faded tapestries depicting ancient scholars debating cosmic truths line the walls between towering bookshelves, their threads unraveling toward the floor.\n\nThree reading tables of heavy mahogany sit scattered about, their surfaces scarred by centuries of quill and ink. Brass fixtures that once held candles now stand empty, their light source long since extinguished. The stained glass windows\u2014your only illumination\u2014depict scenes of cosmic creation, though several panes are cracked or missing entirely, allowing drafts to whisper through the chamber.\n\nThe air itself feels heavy, tasting of mildew and something older, stranger\u2014like the dust of dead languages. Your footsteps echo with surprising loudness on the worn flagstone floor, and you notice the shadows seem deeper here than they should be, as if the light struggles to penetrate the accumulated silence of centuries.\n\nTo your left, a narrow doorway leads further into the archives. Behind you, the passage back to the main library. And directly before you, the mysterious tome continues its faint pulsing glow, its alien symbols seemingly shifting when viewed from the corner of your eye.",
      "actor": "gemini",
